Bake `accelerate` into the image as an always-on runtime dependency.

SGLang's ModelOptModelLoader (srt/model_loader/loader.py -> _load_modelopt_base_model)
imports `accelerate`, and the upstream scitrera/dgx-spark-sglang base image does NOT
ship it. It is triggered by GLM-5-NVFP4 (modelopt base-model load path) and by EAGLE3 /
speculative decoding against a modelopt-quantized target (the draft worker loads the
target's embeddings via _load_modelopt_base_model and ImportErrors without it).

Until now sglang_launch.sh installed it at container start
(`python3 -c "import accelerate" || pip install accelerate`), costing a pip resolve +
download on every GLM-5 / speculative boot. Baking it here turns that guard into a fast
no-op (the launch-script block is kept as belt-and-suspenders for non-baked images).

Mirrors the dockerfile-audio-deps.patch / dockerfile-cutlass-dsl-pin.patch mechanism:
an `ARG ACCELERATE_DEPS` + gated `uv pip install` RUN in the builder stage (BEFORE the
dist-packages split, so it is carried into the runtime stage like the kernels/cutlass
pins). Unlike AUDIO_DEPS the ARG DEFAULTS to "accelerate" so every image gets it even
if a recipe doesn't set the var; a recipe can set ACCELERATE_DEPS="" to opt out.

Anchors on the `# SM121 ... shared memory fix` comment block, so it MUST be applied
AFTER dockerfile-cutlass-dsl-pin.patch (which inserts its block just above the same
anchor). Remove if/when the upstream base image ships accelerate by default.

Apply to: container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly in the local clone of
scitrera/cuda-containers.

--- a/container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly
+++ b/container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly
@@ -292,3 +292,16 @@
+# dgxarley: bake `accelerate` into the image. SGLang's ModelOptModelLoader
+# (_load_modelopt_base_model) imports it; the upstream base image omits it, so
+# GLM-5-NVFP4 and EAGLE/speculative-decode against a modelopt-quantized target
+# would ImportError. Gated by ACCELERATE_DEPS (default "accelerate"; set empty in
+# a recipe to opt out). The sglang_launch.sh `import accelerate || pip install`
+# guard becomes a fast no-op once this is baked. See patches/dockerfile-accelerate.patch.
+ARG ACCELERATE_DEPS="accelerate"
+RUN --mount=type=cache,id=uv-cache,target=/root/.cache/uv \
+    if [ -n "$ACCELERATE_DEPS" ]; then \
+        echo "=== Installing accelerate deps: ${ACCELERATE_DEPS} ==="; \
+        uv pip install ${ACCELERATE_DEPS}; \
+    fi
+
 # SM121 (DGX Spark GB10) shared memory fix for cutlass_moe_fp4.
 # Patches run_fp4_blockwise_scaled_group_mm_sm120() in the JIT-compiled
 # nvfp4_blockwise_moe.cuh to use KernelPtrArrayTmaWarpSpecializedCooperative
